title: Spirit of Mumbai
summary: >-
  Mumbai is the financial capital of India. Being the most visited city of the
  country, it has great healthcare, hospitality, education, business and art
  culture. Filmcity and Bollywood are the attractions while places like
  Elephanta and Gorai are the underrated gems. Business, art, literature,
  history, geography and food are all packed inside the city. This articles
  gives you a breif idea of what Mumbai really is.
